00:27:03.880 --> 00:27:09.640
They told me, OK, good, have a Plan B, C, and D, and get a

00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:17.880
degree. Did you? I did. I studied here in the UK, at

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:21.880
university, but I studied film making. It was a way to please my parents

00:27:21.880 --> 00:27:26.200
but also still be involved somehow in

00:27:26.200 --> 00:27:35.359
film. They must be proud now, though. I understand that.

